## Phase 3 — Neue Pages aus bestehenden Komponenten

### `/admin/security`
Nutzt existierende Enterprise-Tab-Komponenten:
- `TabSecurity.jsx`
- `TabCompliance.jsx`
- `TabGovernanceRules.jsx`
- `TabIncidents.jsx`

### `/admin/backup`
Nutzt existierende Komponenten:
- `BackupManager.jsx`
- `EnterpriseBackupManager.jsx`

### `/admin/improvements`
- `EnterpriseImprovements.jsx` → Route anlegen + in App.jsx importieren

### `/admin/system-check`
- `EnterpriseSystemCheck.jsx` → Route anlegen (ist schon imported!)

---

## Phase 4 — Alte Routes migrieren

### Redirects einrichten (via React Router)

| Alt | Neu | Typ |
|-----|-----|-----|
| `/admin/team-zugriffsrechte` | `/admin/team` | Redirect |
| `/admin/enterprise-control-center` | `/admin/control-center` | Redirect |
| `/admin/enterprise-audit` | `/admin/audit` | Redirect |
| `/admin-logs` | `/admin/audit-logs` | Redirect |
| `/system-logs` | `/admin/logs` | Redirect |
| `/admin/insurance-learning` | `/admin/insurance-learning` | Behalten |

---

## Phase 5 — Orphans einsammeln & Bereinigung

### Pages ohne Route
| Datei | Action |
|-------|--------|
| `EnterpriseImprovements.jsx` | In App.jsx importieren + Route `/admin/improvements` |
| `EnterpriseSystemCheck.jsx` | Route `/admin/system-check` (import existiert bereits!) |

### Komponenten ohne Page
| Komponente | Soll in Page |
|------------|-------------|
| `BackupManager.jsx`, `EnterpriseBackupManager.jsx` | `/admin/backup` |
| `TabSecurity.jsx`, `Compliance`, `GovernanceRules`, `Incidents` | `/admin/security` |
| `SystemTestingDashboard.jsx` | In `/admin/system-check` integrieren |
| `BrokerOpsCleanupPanel.jsx` | In `/admin/control-center` integrieren |

